name: This I Know Print
description:
There are many lessons in life.
Love being one of them.
When you find love, hold on to it. Find meaning; learn to love - for love is one of the greatest gifts of all. ~SIH

The This I Know, I Love You Archival Art Print gets straight in your face and to the point. Present this modern but simple and pleasing print to your favorite person. Text is a medium blue or fuchsia color on a white background. Print can be viewed horizontally and vertically – horizontal is my favorite view!

What you’ll receive:
♥One (1) medium blue or fuchsia colored print measuring 5” X 7” with a .25” border for framing (Signed and dated on the backside)
♥Printed on 100% recycled matte paper with archival inks
♥Thoughtfully packaged in a cello sleeve, with padding for extra strength and shipped flat in sturdy mailer
♥Designed and delivered with love


NOTES:
Please specify print color when ordering.
Frame is not included. (Frame is an IKEA, Ribba Frame)
